  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13078405/adobestock_74125538_edited.jpeg" alt="August Ski Special" data-udi="umb://media/6d8549dacfe54a2583684882295ffb58" /><br />
<p><strong>For the month of August we are offering you 2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire/carriage* in selected hotels.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Offer ending soon - for the last week of this fantastic offer, we have added EXTRA properties across France, Italy and Austria!</strong></p>
<p><strong>France</strong></p>
<p>We have handpicked some great deals for you in <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540" href="/{localLink:umb://document/799f63184c52477c94171a057c16e540}" title="Avoriaz">Avoriaz</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">M<span>é</span>ribel</a>. We have two great new properties <a data-udi="umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6}" title="Hotel Du Golf (Arc 1800)">Hotel du Golf</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil">Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil</a> and for winter 19/20 our popular <a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes">Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes</a> has some exciting changes with the new 'Jacks Bar' opening for this upcoming season. Also we have added some extra properties in <a data-udi="umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40}" title="Hotel Serre Palas">Les Deux Alpes</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd}" title="Hotel Le Val Chaviere">Val Thorens</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704}" title="Hotel Kandahar">Val d'Is<span>é</span>re</a>. </p>
<p><strong>Austria</strong></p>
<p>Check out our hotels in <a data-udi="umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d}" title="Hotel Marietta">Obertauern</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Mayrhofen</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg">Kitzbuhel</a>. All of which are fantastic Half Board properties with easy access to the slopes.</p>
<p><strong>Italy</strong></p>
<p>Check out our hotels in <a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba">Arabba</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/bb8b11b91b9843b4b8642740d3384218" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb8b11b91b9843b4b8642740d3384218}" title="Hotel Antares">Selva</a>, both offering fantastic skiing within The Dolomites, a UNESCO world heritage site.</p>
<p><strong>Take a look at the hotel options below and find the perfect holiday for you - book by 31st August to benefit from these fantastic offers.</strong></p>
