<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>New to Inghams:</strong> This hotel lies in exceptional surroundings, facing Mont Blanc and is located at the foot of the nursery slopes with ski-in/ski-out access, a perfect base to explore the Paradiski area.<br /><br /><strong>2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br /><br />Prices from £799pp<br />Half Board catering including wine with evening meals</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding<br />11/01/20, 01/02/20, 15/02/20 &amp; 29/02/20<br /><br /></em></p>
