<p style="text-align: left;"><span><strong>New to Inghams:</strong> This hotel boasts ski-in, ski-out access as well as fantastic hotel facilities, right in the heart of this quaint car-free resort. An excellent choice for couples, friends or families alike.</span><br /><br /><strong>2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br /><br />Prices from £799pp<br /></strong><strong>Half Board catering including wine with evening meals</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding<br />04/04/20 &amp; 15/02/20<br /><br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Les Cimes du Soleil"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
