<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes"><img src="/media/13077033/meribel_grangettes_ext4.jpg" alt="Fairmont Chateau in Lake Louise" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span><strong>An Inghams favourite:</strong> This Chalet Hotel is perfectly located just across the street from the main Chaudanne ski lifts, within the atmospheric heart of Méribel. New Jacks Bar opens for winter 2019. <br /><br /></span><strong>2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire + <span>€75 bar credit </span>at Jacks Bar</strong><br /><br /><strong>Prices from £749pp</strong><br /><strong>Chalet catering including wine with evening meals</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding<br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;"> 14/12/19, 28/12/19, 04/01/20, 18/01/20, 25/01/20, 15/02/20, 07/03/20, 14/03/20 &amp; 28/03/20</em></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
