<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40}" title="Hotel Serre Palas">Hotel Serre-Palas</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40}" title="Hotel Serre Palas">Les Deux Alpes</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6}" title="Hotel Serre Palas"><img src="/media/13075700/dsc_0453.jpg" alt="Hotel Serre Palas" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></a></p>
<p>Hotel Serre Palas is a quaint family run hotel, situated in the Deux Alpes village centre. The hotel has picturesque mountain views and rooms are comfortable with a warm and welcoming atmosphere. <strong><br /><br /><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br />Prices from £629pp<br />Half Board catering </strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20<br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c3c550acf80e47f1b029fcdd41363f40}" title="Hotel Serre Palas"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd}" title="Hotel Le Val Chaviére">Hotel Le Val Chaviére</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd}" title="Hotel Le Val Chaviere">Val Thorens</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Hotel Le Val Chaviere"><img src="/media/13078812/val-chaviere-vt.jpg" alt="Hotel Le Val Chaviere" data-udi="umb://media/b64a281019ad471f934a2e1832c9c61b" /></a></p>
<p>Run by the charming Garcin family, this hotel is one of our most popular hotels, offering a very warm welcome and a friendly, relaxed atmosphere in a superb ski-in/out location.<strong><br /><br /><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br />Prices from £869pp<br /></strong><strong>Half Board catering </strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20<br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5d004f9809dd4ff1bb330d74cdf902dd}" title="Hotel Le Val Chaviere"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704}" title="Hotel Kandahar">Hotel Kandahar</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704}" title="Hotel Kandahar">Val d'Isere</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Hotel Kandahar"><img src="/media/13078813/hotel-kandahar.jpg" alt="Hotel Kandahar" /></a></p>
<p>The Hotel Kandahar is a genuine alpine retreat. Located just 250m from the slopes, the warm and cosy atmosphere oozes charm, comfort and well-being. A bed &amp; breakfast option is available.<strong><br /><br /><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire </strong><a style="font-weight: bold;" data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Chalet Hotel Les Grangettes"></a><br /><br /><strong>Prices from £1099pp</strong><br /><strong>Half Board Catering</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding<em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;"> 15/02/20</em></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e36f107d1d714fa983952741e524b704}" title="Hotel Kandahar"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<h1 style="text-align: center; line-height: 28px;"><strong>Austria Ski Special - Hotels</strong></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d}" title="Hotel Marietta">Hotel Marietta</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d}" title="Hotel Marietta">Obertauern</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e822554192494e2eb401ed5bb513cee6}" title="Hotel Marietta"><img src="/media/13078814/hotel-marietta.jpg" alt="Hotel Marietta" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></a></p>
<p>The Marietta enjoys an excellent, sunny location close to the resort centre with ski-in/ski-out access and superb spa facilities including indoor pool, and various saunas.<br /><br /><br /><strong><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br />Prices from £859pp<br />Half Board catering </strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20<br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3790038dbe884cd0b3b3755f59e8451d}" title="Hotel Marietta"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Alpenhotel Kramerwirt</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Mayrhofen</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7a167125394045d79758340e629fb7bf}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt"><img src="/media/13078815/may4786_kramerwirt.jpg" alt="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt" data-udi="umb://media/b64a281019ad471f934a2e1832c9c61b" /></a></p>
<p>This picturesque hotel has an excellent reputation for comfort, cuisine and friendly service. It’s located in the centre of Mayrhofen, just a short walk to the gondola stations, with a ski bus stop outside.<br /><br /><strong><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br />Prices from £829pp<br /></strong><strong>Half Board catering </strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20<br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fc64c1eb613b4f1cab95e46539438080}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg">Hotel Schloss Lebenberg</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg">Kitzbuhel</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679" href="/{localLink:umb://document/19e0226cec264ce2ac16c6d8433a5679}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg"><img src="/media/13078816/hotel-schloss-lebenberg.jpg" alt="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg" /></a></p>
<p>Hotel Schloss Lebenburg is a fairy tale retreat that allows you to get a flavour of 17th century architecture while living in modern comforts and luxuries, such as a panoramic rooftop pool that provides stunning views of the town.<br /><br /><strong>2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire </strong><br /><br /><strong>Prices from £1039pp</strong><br /><strong>Half Board catering</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding<em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;"> 15/02/20</em></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2b9dfe5ae00a456081b4078b0d1acae6}" title="Hotel Schloss Lebenberg"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div> </div>
<h1 style="text-align: center; line-height: 28px;"><strong>Italy Ski Special - Hotels</strong></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba">Sporthotel Arrabba</a><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba">Arabba</a></h3>
