<p>This hotel has all the fine qualities of a true Alpine hotel with touches of luxury thrown in. The Sport Hotel Arabba prides itself on personal service, attention to detail and fine dining.<strong><br /><br />2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br /><br />Prices from £1069pp<br />Half Board catering</strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20 <br /><br /><br /></em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4d6207c810248fdb2d181e97a44755f}" title="Sport Hotel Arabba"><strong>Find out more &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
