<p>In the centre of Selva, close to all amenities and above all the ski lifts, Hotel Antares offers excellent leisure facilities and easy access to the slopes, with the Ciampinoi gondola just 200m away.<br /><br /><strong>2 for 1 lift passes + 50% off ski hire<br /><br /><br />Prices from £1049pp<br /></strong><strong>Half Board catering </strong><br /><em style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 12px!important;">Valid on all dates excluding 15/02/20<br /><br /><br /></em></p>
